## 261. Graph Valid Tree

思路：当且仅当边数量 = 节点数量 - 1并且整图只有一块连通时，图可以转换为树。

```
def validTree(self, n: int, edges: List[List[int]]) -> bool:
        if len(edges) != n - 1:
            return False
        seen = set()
        dq = collections.deque()
        graph = [set() for _ in range(n)]
        for i, j in edges:
            graph[i].add(j)
            graph[j].add(i)
        seen.add(0)
        dq.append(0)
        while dq:
            cur = dq.popleft()
            for cand in graph[cur]:
                if cand not in seen:
                    dq.append(cand)
                    seen.add(cand)
        return len(seen) == n
``` 
